modShortDescription: An xml edit that Dualboot made that should remove feral and irradiated zombies. This also includes demolition zombies, screamers and wights.
modDescription:
An xml edit that Dualboot made that should remove feral and irradiated [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/). This also includes demolition zombies, screamers and wights.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KkbP0D8rEKsiQcvEWeV2QINhejFE0_Jr/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/26208-alpha-20-no-feral-irradiated-zombies/).

**Credits:** Dualboot
